title: NFL ATL: Coaching carousel and Best of 2013
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Coaching carousel and Best of 2013
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling -- dissects the changing coaching landscape following the conclusion of Week 17 action.  The heroes also share what they loved most about the 2013 regular season, as well as what they are looking forward to next year. Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
